<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF109-660-773  </DOCNO><DOCID>09 660 773.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>The Seybold Report on Publishing Systems  Nov 26 1990 v20 n6p34(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Seybold Publications Inc. 1990.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Rastec enhances Pixact system. (System Peripherals, Extensions andOther Items)andM;</TITLE><DESCRIPT>Company:   Rastec (Product introduction).andO;Product:   Rastec Pixact RS (Scanning device) (Product introduction).andO;Topic:     Product IntroductionScanning Devices.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>Rastec Enhances Pixact system Rastec, which has been selling ablack-and-white flatbed scanning system consisting of a Pixact scanner, animagesetter and an online processor, enhanced the system with a link to apagination or image-handling system.andP;  The standalone Pixact SA systemconsists of the scanner and one of four imagesetters (Ultre and Linotronicmachines, both in narrow and wide versions).andM;The next model--the RS--includes options such as borders, effect screens,duotones, dot-gain correction, an online densitometer and the possibility ofadding a SCSI interface.andP;  Both the SA and RS models scan positivetransparencies in black-and-white or color, in sizes from 18mm X 24mm to 4&quot; X5&quot;.andM;The top-of-the-line RT model is an Rs with the additional capability ofscanning negative transparencies.andM;At IFRA, Rastec introduced a SCSI interface and the ability to generate TIFFfiles, which means that they now can be connected directly to Macintoshes orPCs handling TIFF files.andP;  For a Mac environment, the scanner connectsdirectly to the Mac's SCSI port.andP;  For a PC, the scanner comes with a SCSIboard that has to be installed in a customer-supplied PC.andM;Rastec said that between 20 and 30 of its scanners have been installed andare in production.andP;  The scanners are priced at DKK 580,000 ($103,000) for theRS and DKK600,000 ($106,000) for the RT.andP;  That puts them in competition withthe ECRM Autokon, which is well entrenched around the world.andP;  It also pitsthem against the new crop of desktop-oriented devices with nearly as manyfeatures and much lower prices.andP;  So whether the new SCSI feature will have asignificant impact on sales remains to be seen.andO;</TEXT></DOC>